Helping Out

There are two ways you can help out. By creating icons or submitting suggestions.

Become a Contributor

Becoming a contributor is easy, submit 5 icons and you will recieve an invite where you can manage and add new icons.

Submit Five Icons

Icon Suggestions

Contributors are always looking for new ideas, help out by submitting a suggestion on GitHub.
